snippet.title: Singularity - Battle AI Gone Rogue - Exclusive to Zero Latency VR
snippet.description:
https://zerolatencyvr.com/games/singularity/

Enter an immersive, sci-fi adventure on a station stranded in the depths of space. Fight to the death against killer robots as you explore narrow corridors, treacherous lifts and zero-gravity environments. You will need to work together with your squad to get out alive, with the answers you're looking for.
